  "body": "### Component\n\nCast\n\n### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?\n\n- [ ] Foundry\n- [ ] Foundryup\n\n### What version of Foundry are you on?\n\n_No response_\n\n### What command(s) is the bug in?\n\n_No response_\n\n### Operating System\n\n_No response_\n\n### Describe the bug\n\nthe --cast-async flag is currently undocumented and it is not clear what it is for\r\n\r\nmaybe this is some ported legacy flag (dapp)?\r\n\r\n\r\n```console\r\ncast send --help\r\n\r\n        --cast-async\r\n            [env: CAST_ASYNC=]\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\nlooking at where it's used\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/blob/7c96807294f51c121f1a2d614b55055bc7cb126c/cli/src/cast.rs#L408-L409\r\n\r\nit's clear what it does: not waiting for the receipt.\r\n\r\nimo we should reevaluate the naming here as well, maybe something like `--no-wait` `--async`?",
